  <title>Dùng chuột thuận tay trái</title>

  <p>Bạn có thể đảo hai phím trái và phải của chuột hoặc touchpad để tiện dùng hơn nếu thuận tay trái.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Open the <gui xref="shell-introduction#activities">Activities</gui> overview and
      start typing <gui>Mouse &amp; Touchpad</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click on <gui>Mouse &amp; Touchpad</gui> to open the panel.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>In the <gui>General</gui> section, switch <gui>Primary button</gui>
      to <gui>Right</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note>
    <p>This setting will affect both your mouse and touchpad, as well as any
    other pointing device.</p>
  </note>

